               <p>
                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="178709120100"></xptr>The prisoner was seen taking the shalloon, and immediately pursued, and taken with the property; when he was taken, he said to the prosecutor, will you take me before the Justice for stealing a piece of shalloon?</p>
               <p>The prisoner called two witnesses to his character, who said he kept a sale-shop in Houndsditch.</p>
